title: #92Noon! KdSA/Leber/Spielman/Korzo
description: Kyndra de St Aubin gets us rolling on the return of MLS, Ben Leber in studio, Vikings GM Rick Spielman on the team's approach to issues of equality and diversity in our community, and Korzo breaks down everything for us in the final hour!
